#### [NEW] [ElectronicProductController.java](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/My%20service/Easycart%202.1/backend/src/main/java/com/easycart/sme/controller/ElectronicProductController.java)
Define REST endpoints:
- `GET /api/electronics/active`: Public endpoint. Fetches active products created within the last 3 days (`Instant.now().minus(3, ChronoUnit.DAYS)`), returning up to 3 products.
- `GET /api/admin/electronics`: Admin-only endpoint. Fetches all electronic products so admins can view past/expired entries.
- `POST /api/admin/electronics`: Admin-only endpoint. Creates a new electronic product post.
- `DELETE /api/admin/electronics/{id}`: Admin-only endpoint. Deletes a product post by ID.

